title: War of the Roses: He Was Trying to Get Through the Alphabet
description: Stacy learned when she first started dating her boyfriend Steve that he was trying to "get with" a girl from every letter of the alphabet.  Stacy doesn't have the evidence to prove he's cheating but she also knows he hasn't gotten with a girl from every letter of the alphabet yet so she's wondering if that's still a goal of his!
